  "texts": [
    "This enduring engagement underlines the utility and user-friendliness of CaiTI, as well as its potential to maintain user interest and interaction over extended periods.",
    "Quantitative AnalysisChatBot Usability Scale (BUS-15) is a recently developed tool to assess end-users' satisfaction with chatbots [17].",
    "Taking BUS-15 into account, we devised the 10 aspects listed in Table 8.",
    "Subjects rated the system from 1 (poor) to 5 (excellent) for these 10 aspects on the first and last day of the experiment.",
    "In general, subjects gave high ratings to CaiTI."
  ]
}